name: r-gggenes
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set version = "0.4.1" %}
{% set posix = 'm2-' if win else '' %}
{% set native = 'm2w64-' if win else '' %}

package:
  name: r-gggenes
  version: {{ version|replace("-", "_") }}

source:
  url:
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/gggenes_{{ version }}.tar.gz
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/Archive/gggenes/gggenes_{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: 53a29d35d7169af18926e54a6adfa1bbcf09624cf40c109734841bf0c4b793e8

build:
  merge_build_host: true  # [win]
  number: 0
  noarch: generic
  rpaths:
    - lib/R/lib/
    - lib/

requirements:
  build:
    - {{ posix }}zip               # [win]
  host:
    - r-base
    - r-ggfittext >=0.8.0
    - r-ggplot2 >=2.2.1
    - r-rlang >=0.2.0
  run:
    - r-base
    - r-ggfittext >=0.8.0
    - r-ggplot2 >=2.2.1
    - r-rlang >=0.2.0

test:
  commands:
    - $R -e "library('gggenes')"           # [not win]
    - "\"%R%\" -e \"library('gggenes')\""  # [win]

about:
  home: https://wilkox.org/gggenes
  license: GPL-2.0-only
  summary: Provides a 'ggplot2' geom and helper functions for drawing gene arrow maps.
  license_family: GPL2
  license_file:
    - {{ environ["PREFIX"] }}/lib/R/share/licenses/GPL-2

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - conda-forge/r
